{"tid":2400566,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百名學生須檢疫 梁子超質疑：工作場所比試場風險更高，為何不用同一原則？","createTime":"2021-02-09T05:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T15:10:19.000Z","uid":5195,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0a44a53317052c49930ef29125a1a5b4aeddc668","tid":2400566,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"對於逾百名學生須檢疫，呼吸系統科專科醫生梁子超認為，一般學校在試場採取嚴謹防疫措施，學生須戴口罩及分開坐，風險較低，兩名確診學生在校沒明顯接觸史，暫無證據顯示校內有傳播。被問當局做法是否太嚴，他說對此「有疑問」，形容做法是「寧枉勿縱」，認為可安排學生密集式檢測，非全部檢疫。至於共用設施風險，他說雖有風險，但質疑考試期間不會所有學生都如廁或多次如廁。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超又說，<span class=\"red\">工作場所比試場風險更高，員工長時間逗留，更多共用設施，倘試場有兩宗確診所有考生便須檢疫，反問為何較高風險的工作場所不用同一原則。</span>"},{"pid":"f9977e0c3db924bedc2ea09a1a786ba0cab2f9fb","tid":2400566,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"黎先生.jgp"},{"pid":"fee2e90ec4b5ecc4209ce6a8286a4b3e2655318d","tid":2400566,"uid":89382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9977e0c3db924bedc2ea09a1a786ba0cab2f9fb","tid":2400566,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"黎先生.jgp"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.jpg"},{"pid":"b9806e9e885e5a8bbbb176d10e1bb0e3b459970a","tid":2400566,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"呢件廢老第一次唔係講廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50848aa8c45565a47507aa3ae0aaae0372252d31","tid":2400566,"uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f9977e0c3db924bedc2ea09a1a786ba0cab2f9fb","tid":2400566,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"黎先生.jgp"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=